To see the outcome of her patient wiles:

How Circe's guests have sunk to shameful sleep, As sailors perish in the yawning deep ;

And how anon the tortured liver wakes

To sudden protest5 how the stomach zachee, While steaming sweat bedews the trembling umbe, And a thick mist the bloodshot vision dims. With the wrecked body brought to such a pase, Shall Gluttony essay beyond? Alae!

Her arte would seek to bury in the sod

Even the soul—spark of the breath of G0d1
